{"tid":558003,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都有皮膚敏感？","createTime":"2018-02-12T01:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T00:56:54.000Z","uid":31531,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b5a7643fff68eb02a028ef468e58031cda0d0caf","tid":558003,"uid":31531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:32:50.000Z","msg":"皮膚敏感好嚴重<br />\n長期都紅，痕，無論面定身都有<br />\n試過敏感到塊面腫埋<br />\n最嚴重試過敏感性休克，內外都敏感搞到要入廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟有冇得斷尾<br />\n唔想成日都又紅又痕<br />\n好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc8dad1f22cb377ca02dd6e421c6243b45a8ec0","tid":558003,"uid":31531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:33:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aafc8755dbb9ded5602517c8be57e1bee5d83dfe","tid":558003,"uid":44440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:38:49.000Z","msg":"做血液測試先啦"},{"pid":"028661f7a649fd7e09e1c71ca0ed5db58cc8d929","tid":558003,"uid":31531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aafc8755dbb9ded5602517c8be57e1bee5d83dfe","tid":558003,"uid":44440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:38:49.000Z","msg":"做血液測試先啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T02:26:36.000Z","msg":"要去醫院做？"},{"pid":"1186d9544b393447b02d5f20bb9faec94ac7e8ef","tid":558003,"uid":31531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T14:38:56.000Z","msg":"想問睇中醫有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4061dab3c2310c44403a114616873da27f148c","tid":558003,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1186d9544b393447b02d5f20bb9faec94ac7e8ef","tid":558003,"uid":31531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T14:38:56.000Z","msg":"想問睇中醫有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20